   <text>
      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Geographical Society of ¶ AUSTRALASIA. ¶ INSTITUTED 1883 ¶ NEW SOUTH WALES BRANCH. ¶ ....</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">88.04.26</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Theodore Bevan</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">A38 Royal Geographical Society of Australasia (Vic. Branch) papers, Mitchell Library, State Library of New South Wales, Sydney.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Newspaper clippings attached to the MS express the Society's appreciation of Bevan's significant explorations in New Guinea, and that of others (<seg style="font-style: italic; ">Sydney morning herald</seg>, 21 April 1888, p. 10; <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Daily telegraph</seg>, 21 April 1888, p. 9; and <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Daily telegraph</seg>, 26 April 1888, p. 5).</p>
               </note>
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">
                  <seg style="font-variant: small-caps; ">Geographical Society of</seg>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">AUSTRALASIA.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">
                  <seg style="font-size: 10pt; ">INSTITUTED 1883</seg>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">
                  <seg style="font-size: 10pt; ">NEW SOUTH WALES BRANCH.</seg>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Montefiore Joseph Co</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">4 O'Connell St. <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Sydney</hi>
               </seg>.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">Sydney </seg>26 April <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">188</seg>8</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">My dear Baron von Mueller,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I was indeed pleased to receive this morning your valued letter<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Letter not found.</p>
               </note> written as you alone know how to write. I look forward with interest to your Presidential address. It is unfortunate that you should be unduly overwhelmed with work but I suppose such is the invariable penalty attaching under our modern civilization to pre-eminence in any line of life; and especially so in the case of an almost unique specialist scientist like yourself.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>To myself as you know a life of activity rather than one permitting profound research has been allotted; and should I have opportunities for further geographical exploitation I trust to be able to make better and less economical arrangements, and have some collector with me who may bring grist to your mill.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>By the by I sent copy of pamphlet<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Bevan (1888) a 'preliminary presentation pamphlet', 'limited to 100 copies' contains numerous extracts from the press and other supportive statements.</p>
               </note> to your correspondent Herr Wichmann Co-Editor Petermann's Mittheilungen Gotha<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">i.e. <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Petermann's geographische Mitteilungen</seg>.</p>
               </note> who wrote me a nice letter some few months ago; and spoke of hearing of my work through your good self</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">yours sincerely</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Theodore Bevan</p>
         </div>
      </body>
